quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  29,26,"Nuko Lutwi (Loti) yemera ubutumwa bwa Ibrahimu. Maze (Ibrahimu) aravuga ati “Nimukiye kwa Nyagasani wanjye kuko ari Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye.”"
  29,27,"Maze (Ibrahimu) tumuha impano (yo kubyara) Isihaqa (Isaka) na Yaqubu (Yakobo). Nuko dushyira mu rubyaro rwe ubuhanuzi n’ibitabo. Tunamuha ibihembo bye hano ku isi (mu kuvugwa neza n’abantu bose), kandi ku munsi w’imperuka azaba ari mu ntungane"
  29,28,Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Lutwi yabwiraga abantu be ati “Mu by’ukuri murakora ibikorwa by’urukozasoni bitigeze bikorwa n’uwo ari we wese mu biremwa.”
  29,29,"Ese koko mukora ubutinganyi n’abagabo (nkamwe), mugategera abantu ku nzira mugamije ubugizi bwa nabi, mukanakorera ibibi mu byicaro byanyu? Nta kindi cyabaga igisubizo cy’abantu be uretse kuvuga bati “Ngaho tuzanire ibihano bya Allah niba koko uri umwe mu banyakuri!”"
  29,30,(Lutwi) aravuga ati “Nyagasani! Ntsindira abantu b’abangizi.”
  29,31,"Maze ubwo intumwa zacu (Abamalayika) zageraga kuri Ibrahimu zimuzaniye inkuru nziza, zaravuze ziti “Mu by’ukuri tugiye kurimbura abatuye uyu mudugudu, kuko rwose abawutuye ari inkozi z’ibibi.”"
  29,32,"(Ibrahimu) aravuga ati “Ariko (muzirikane ko) harimo Lutwi!” Baravuga bati “Twe tuzi neza abawurimo, rwose turamurokorana n’umuryango we, usibye umugore we uribube mu basigara (mu bihano).”"
  29,33,"Nuko ubwo Intumwa zacu zageraga kwa Lutwi, byamuteye agahinda ahagarika umutima (atinya ko na zo zakorerwa ibya mfurambi), maze ziravuga ziti “Ntugire ubwoba ndetse ntunagire agahinda! Rwose turakurokorana n’umuryango wawe usibye umugore wawe uri busigare (mu bihano).”"
  29,34,Mu by’ukuri turamanurira igihano giturutse mu kirere ku batuye uyu mudugudu kubera ubwononnyi bakora
  29,35,Ni n’uko rwose twawusizemo ikimenyetso kigaragara ku bantu bafite ubwenge
  29,36,"N’abantu b’i Mediyani twaboherereje umuvandimwe wabo Shuwayibu. Aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimugaragire Allah, kandi mwizere (ibihembo byanyu) ku munsi w’imperuka. Ndetse ntimugakwize ubwangizi ku isi.”"
  29,37,"Nuko baramuhinyura maze baterwa n’umutingito ukaze, bahinduka imirambo bapfukamye mu mazu yabo"
  29,38,"Kandi (twarimbuye) abantu bo mu bwoko bwa Adi n’abo mu bwoko bwa Thamudu, ndetse rwose ibyo byabagaragariye ku mazu yabo (yabaye amatongo). Shitani yanabakundishije ibikorwa byabo (bibi) maze abakumira kugana inzira y’ukuri, kandi mu by’ukuri bari abanyabwenge"
  29,39,"(Twanarimbuye) Qaruna, Farawo na Hamana. Kandi rwose Musa yabazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara, ariko bagaragaje ubwibone ku isi; nyamara ntibaducitse"
  29,40,"Bityo, buri tsinda twarihaniye ibyaha byaryo; muri bo hari abo twoherereje inkubi y’umuyaga uvanze n’amabuye (abantu ba Lutwi), hari abakubiswe n’urusaku rw’ibihano (abantu ba Swalehe n’aba Shuwayibu), hari abo twarigitishije mu butaka (Qaruna), ndetse hari n’abo twarohamishije (abantu ba Nuhu na Farawo n’ingabo ze). Kandi Allah ntiyigeze abarenganya, ahubwo ni bo ubwabo bihemukiye"
  29,41,Urugero rw’abashyize ibigirwamana mu cyimbo cya Allah (biringiye ko hari icyo byabamarira) ni nk’igitagangurirwa cyiyubakiye inzu (cyiringiye ko ikomeye nta cyagihungabanya); ariko mu by’ukuri inzu yoroshye kurusha izindi ni inzu y’igitagangurirwa; iyaba bari babizi
  29,42,"Mu by’ukuri Allah azi ibyo basaba bitari We. Kandi (Allah) ni Umunyembaraga, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  29,43,"N’izo ni ingero duha abantu, ariko nta bandi bazisobanukirwa usibye abamenyi"
  29,44,Allah yaremye ibirere n’isi mu kuri. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ikimenyetso ku bemera
  29,45,"Soma ibyo wahishuriwe mu gitabo (Qur’an), unahozeho iswala; mu by’ukuri iswala zibuza gukora ibiteye isoni n’ibibi. Kandi rwose gusingiza Allah biruta byose; ndetse Allah azi ibyo mukora"